    "description": "<strong>我们希望有更多热爱这类型游戏的朋友们可以参与到试玩并给出任何游戏反馈，大家的支持是团队的最大动力！感谢！<br><br>《魔法符石》交流QQ群：945567029</strong><br><br><strong>在魔法符石中你将扮演不同的角色在在各个房间中奋勇杀敌。你可以通过搭配不同的技能和装备，选择独特的专属技能打造出独一无二的角色。丰富的技能和装备，独特的祝福和珍宝都会给你来带来刺激、惊险的游戏体验。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206200/extras/547f694e647f05547455e44804afb554.avif?t=1772255266\" width=620 height=76 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206200/extras/7078c24500e1a69fa17b92a3e72e6f53.avif?t=1772255266\" width=614 height=224 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206200/extras/ec9af7fa8a79bc0c506cee3f9964e382.poster.avif?t=1772255266\" width=614 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206200/extras/ec9af7fa8a79bc0c506cee3f9964e382.webm?t=1772255266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206200/extras/ec9af7fa8a79bc0c506cee3f9964e382.mp4?t=1772255266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>每一名角色都拥有一个专属技能槽位，不同的角色拥有不同的专属技能。每名角色也都拥有一个专属的专属技能升级页面。玩家可以通过不同的祝福来解锁选择不同流派的专属技能。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206200/extras/5529941c17b3509888543cdd8bca0e8e.avif?t=1772255266\" width=620 height=76 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206200/extras/867af35f7dee2e10209aedb383dee9b1.avif?t=1772255266\" width=776 height=136 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206200/extras/f7e5137aaee11a8603785d18fdaf1c4f.poster.avif?t=1772255266\" width=614 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206200/extras/f7e5137aaee11a8603785d18fdaf1c4f.webm?t=1772255266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206200/extras/f7e5137aaee11a8603785d18fdaf1c4f.mp4?t=1772255266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>每名角色都有4个通用技能槽位，通用技能可以在游戏过程中通过技能石选择不同的技能进行装备。每个通用技能都可以通过祝福提升其等级。技能升级后可以显著提升其威力和表现，部分技能还能改变其机制。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206200/extras/588b5d4bb54460fbb89ab3c06ac711ff.avif?t=1772255266\" width=620 height=76 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206200/extras/5503a47ed9deb48e88a7ad7077138d8b.avif?t=1772255266\" width=614 height=136 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206200/extras/0cc3d5631e2286ef24658dbc522bbac8.poster.avif?t=1772255266\" width=614 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206200/extras/0cc3d5631e2286ef24658dbc522bbac8.webm?t=1772255266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206200/extras/0cc3d5631e2286ef24658dbc522bbac8.mp4?t=1772255266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>每个角色都可以携带最多9件装备。装备有4个不同的稀有度，稀有度越高提供的属性加成越高，有些还会有一些特殊效果。装备除了提供属性加成还提供祝福，玩家可以根据自己的需求选择不同类型的装备自由搭配。<br>珍宝是游戏内用于提升玩家一些输出或生存的一些宝物。玩家可以通过珍宝的效果与装备、祝福搭配尝试不同的套路和流派。</strong>",
